    "attributes": {
        "action": "Replace RE with 'Equality and acceptance' in the national curriculum ",
        "additional_details": "I think hidden disabilities aren\u2019t often spoken about like they should be, and I believe if \u201cReligious education\u201d was changed to \u201cEquality and acceptance\u201d children would be taught about hidden disabilities and how everyone is different but deserves to be accepted for who they are. I want religion and hidden disabilities to be one subject about how everyone is different but everyone matters just the same.",
        "background": "I would like religious education within school settings to be changed to equality and acceptance and have the subject around not just religion but hidden disabilities. I want it to be a subject that informs kids about all kinds of equality and to accept children for who they are.",
